{"tid":1489071,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非回合] 西灣河 / 太古 / 天后 / 跑馬地 同時放映","createTime":"2019-08-19T19:15:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T02:01:17.000Z","uid":294095,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e140708531ccefb8f745f70095bde132c3958f7d","tid":1489071,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:15:55.000Z","msg":"全靠各位街坊同巴絲支持，放映會由<span style=\"color: red;\">一晚1個變左一晚4個</span>，希望可以更多區同時播放，<span style=\"color: red;\">遍地開花</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HzrpQR0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHzrpQR0.png&h=6384d5c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K2sAc5o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK2sAc5o.png&h=5228356c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SxijELq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSxijELq.png&h=b4f1c8b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fd8cfiM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffd8cfiM.png&h=d7c4eca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ECdF5o4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FECdF5o4.png&h=f450066a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點擊連結: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/fundraise_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Ffundraise_hk&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=2b288ab9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/fundraise_hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>做咩要搞連儂放映會?</strong></span></span><br />\n而家未能有效說服藍絲或中游分子，主因係各執一詞，佢地用<span style=\"color: red;\">TVB視角</span>去批判示威者，甚至支持黑社會胡亂打人。<br />\n<br />\n我地要俾佢地知道<span style=\"color: red;\">真相</span>，所以喺佢地樓下搞放映會，播放其他傳媒既片段，等佢地自己思考誰對誰錯<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我地搞過啲咩?</strong></span></span><br />\n籌左少少錢，買左兩套裝備，去左好幾區試播，亦有群組兄弟自發搞放映會<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k5trgwg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk5trgwg.jpg&h=70d8172e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BQO60XW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBQO60XW.jpg&h=5dc75b27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g4Zqw4C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg4Zqw4C.jpg&h=52d4e3e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n3gkkXX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn3gkkXX.jpg&h=e13a8ff1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9zqtuRi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9zqtuRi.jpg&h=a2e165d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YpxzqpD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYpxzqpD.jpg&h=1c23e098&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>搞放映會有咩好處?</strong></span></span><br />\n- 游說非同溫層既群眾<br />\n- 人力成本低，每次只需1-2人去管理一個放映<br />\n- 風險較小，最多被人告阻街<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>搞放映會有咩唔好處?</strong></span></span><br />\n- 每個放映站只能接觸某範圍內市民<br />\n- 裝備成本高 (有關裝備可以去Funding Page 睇到: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/fundraise_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Ffundraise_hk&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=2b288ab9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/fundraise_hk</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>點解要集資?</strong></span></span><br />\n1. 增加放映會既物資，同一時間可以多個地方同時放映<br />\n2. 增加放映會既覆蓋區域，想做到全港18區甚至每個地鐵站都有<br />\n3. 提供放映物資俾各個集會<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點樣可以支持?</span></span></strong><br />\n- 上去我地眾籌 campaign 募捐 (<a href=\"http://bit.ly/fundraise_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Ffundraise_hk&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=2b288ab9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/fundraise_hk</a>)<br />\n- 有額外既 Projector 去捐贈俾我地"},{"pid":"8cb549b1bf533c3f8742d098df15b2d1bc0c1e93","tid":1489071,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:17:27.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2a4cfe66fb0125c21aa09480a0023441647e5c","tid":1489071,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:20:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9345ad1c787dab3650c2587ab23b4eba1e95d177","tid":1489071,"uid":308878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:22:22.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81de1b7b2c97b11e092c1841edd231857d6e190b","tid":1489071,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:24:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f8d474eeb89bf01caac386c5cc288928a70365","tid":1489071,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:27:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f7cdf317aba9c1e862759a59fec251e25fb7fe","tid":1489071,"uid":270423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:28:00.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"f6bfc1cc569e01cf34780d38af3fc096073b4fc5","tid":1489071,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0